channel.title: Help With Auto cache downloader?
channel.description:
Can someone help me with an Auto Cache downloader?
I'm using Hybrid PvP client and it seems to have some of the things needed for an auto downloader but it doesn't work so I don't know what bits I haven't got. I also need help Jaring it to make a webclient because when I jar it after I run it, it downloads nulled cache files. I'm not sure if that has to do with the auto downloader or the jaring. Please help.
ALSO This isn't as important but does anyone know how I can do a top 5 Pkers list (based on kills) and a menu to show your kills and deaths?
